{{Quote|Step back, little Butterfly... I know eight forms of '''Tae-Jitsu'''...|[[Buck]]|<ref name="Qui-Gon and Obi-Wan: The Aurorient Express 2">[[Qui-Gon and Obi-Wan: The Aurorient Express 2|''Qui-Gon and Obi-Wan: The Aurorient Express'' 2]]</ref>}}
'''Tae-Jitsu''' was a martial arts style. [[Phow Ji]] once stated that he was a master of this style.<ref name="Battle Surgeons">''[[MedStar I: Battle Surgeons]]''</ref>

The eco-terrorist [[Buck]] claimed to know eight forms of this style. Apparently it was practiced by the Jedi Order as well, as a young [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] easily defeated Buck, afterward commenting on his good form, but lack of balance.

